title: Home.And.Away.2014.05.06.mp4
description:
Home & Away 6th May 2014

My apologies for the absence. Due to the high nature of uploading/downloading I do, I found myself running out of allowable data given to me by my internet provider over the last few months, which resulted in going over the limit and having my speed slowed down. For that reason I took an extended break from uploading shows. I am currently looking into changing internet providers so that I can continue to provide these shows for others to enjoy.

Thank you all for your patience.
